<br>
If shield bashing,  &lt;--not 2handed or kick or slam, had it's taunt valued tied to that of the paladins' stun spell, then this would basicaly inprove the three tank classes tanking and nerf the monk tanking more things then currently.  Of corse the rangers might slip into more tank slots?<br>
