All in all I'd agree with this new ability only if it did three things<br>
1 Only useable by paladin/warrior/shadowknight.<br>
2 Gave bash the same taunt value as the &quot;stun&quot; spell.  &lt;-- a nice taunt value.<br>
3 The blocking was slightly better for warriors. &lt;-- 10% advantage to the warrior's avoidance over pal/sk.<br>
<br>
This still keeps the warrior a better raid tank and increases the gap between the non tanks and keeps a margin of better tanking done by warriors over the knights.<br>
<br>
Right now the non large warriors are usualy under useing gehto bashing.  Kick is for raids when trying not to get aggroed.  bash/slam is for more aggro.<br>
